00:04:16.070 --> 00:04:17.579
So that's what happened.

00:04:17.579 --> 00:04:19.298
That's how that came about.

00:04:19.298 --> 00:04:21.589
That's the first time I'd
ever done anything like that,

00:04:21.589 --> 00:04:24.110
